{
  "$description": "Dark-theme overrides — ONLY the semantic color layer is repointed at different primitives; primitives, radius, typography and motion are NOT duplicated. Emitted into the `.dark` block of tokens.css. Every semantic color role is emitted in `.dark`; a role omitted here inherits its light value (e.g. `muted-2`, `header-foreground`, `primary-surface`, `tint-foreground` is overridden, but roles like `muted-2` intentionally carry the light neutral). The neo-brutalist dark surface inverts the frame (white structural border on near-black), lifts the button to a light-blue fill with dark ink, and flips the cast-shadow tones lighter.",
